README.MD

This project is a RESTful API built using Node.js and Express.js. It simulates a social media platform similar to 
Instagram, managing resources such as users, posts, comments, likes, and followers.
The API follows REST principles with proper URI design, HTTP methods, status codes, and content negotiation.

Objectives
Design RESTful API endpoints
Implement CRUD operations
Use correct HTTP methods and status codes
Handle requests and responses properly
Implement content negotiation
Document API endpoints

🛠️ Technologies Used
Node.js
Express.js
Morgan (logging)
CORS
Helmet (security)
Nodemon (development)

Pojected structure
